<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢١٤ - نا مَعْمَرٌ ,<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ الزُّهْرِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَنْ كَانَ عَلَى يَوْمٍ أَوْ نَحْوِهِ فَهُوَ كَأَهْلِ مَكَّةَ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>